出或預留的輪椅人士座位會於當日上午十時起，在香港體育館售票處，以及城市售票網的其他售票渠道，包括網上購票(<a href=\"http://www.urbtix.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbtix.hk&d=ZchohgaxB9QG9V%2BAmERvXdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d3599ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.urbtix.hk</a>)、流動購票應用程式My URBTIX (Android 及 iPhone/iPad 版) 及信用卡電話購票熱線(852) 2111 5999發售，供所有人士購買。購票者每次最多可購買2張即日門票。<br />\n票務資料 2:\t即日門票信用卡購票限制（適用於網上及流動應用程式購票）<br />\n顧客透過網上或流動應用程式購買此節目的即日門票時，當使用同一信用卡的累計購票數量在任何一次交易中已達2張上限，該信用卡即不能再於同日用作購買此節目的即日門票。此項信用卡購票限制或會因應售票情況而放寬而不作另行通知。"},{"pid":"855d79d411cf4e12b7ac248f9a5a38b0850aacee","tid":632980,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人炒先算"},{"pid":"8945e11e65d51d6abc577165fc4fb6010f00bb58","tid":632980,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"大量正位可購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/105423_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F105423_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=bc1d972c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/105427_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F105427_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=c9423d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a829f8834098cca4d20a59f7771a17aa80bd65fb","tid":632980,"uid":81625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"想睇，我見仲有大把飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如有好位放出黎可以搵我"},{"pid":"89e55d58ca76a40eb75e837edb964d7dc44455d1","tid":632980,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a829f8834098cca4d20a59f7771a17aa